3) throwing an exception
   throw new IllegalArgumentException();
4) convert String to char array using str.toCharArray() as its faster
5) 

Numbers:
1) How to check for overflow
   rev > Integer.MAX_VALUE/10 || (rev == Integer.MAX_VALUE / 10 && pop > 7)
   rev < Integer.MIN_VALUE/10 || (rev == Integer.MIN_VALUE / 10 && pop < -8)
   where pop = pop * 10 + (num%10);
2) How to half numbers:
   Use palindrome logic
   When length is odd --> get rid of the middle digit by dividing reversedNum / 10
3) 

Stack:
1) Never remove/peek value from stack without checking if its non-empty